      <title>Meloni 将为 G7 峰会召集一群才华横溢的人物</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/meloni-invites-milei-lula-erdogan-pope-to-g-7-summit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼有望在下个月的七国集团峰会上策划阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱与巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦之间的首次总统会晤，而教皇也将首次出席此次峰会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/meloni-invites-milei-lula-erdogan-pope-to-g-7-summit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 14:28:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>甘茨政党提议投票解散以色列议会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/gantz-s-party-proposes-vote-to-dissolve-israel-s-parliament</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列战时内阁成员本尼·甘茨的政党表示，希望解散议会，以迫使提前举行选举并罢免总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/gantz-s-party-proposes-vote-to-dissolve-israel-s-parliament</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 14:20:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>祖马政党表示对南非任何联盟都持开放态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/zuma-s-party-signals-it-s-open-to-any-coalitions-in-south-africa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非前总统雅各布·祖马领导的政党表示愿意与志同道合的竞争对手达成联盟协议，该政党在全国选举中赢得了足够的支持，帮助消除执政党非洲人国民大会的多数席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/zuma-s-party-signals-it-s-open-to-any-coalitions-in-south-africa</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 13:34:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷克警告称乌克兰弹药计划资金不足</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/czechs-warn-funding-is-lagging-on-ammunition-plan-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克一名高级官员敦促盟友加大对向乌克兰运送弹药计划的融资，并表示，在做出承诺的国家中，只有四分之一真正实现了融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/czechs-warn-funding-is-lagging-on-ammunition-plan-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 13:28:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将在峰会前访问法国与马克龙会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/biden-to-visit-france-for-meeting-with-macron-ahead-of-summits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙将于下周会见美国总统乔·拜登，两国领导人寻求加强在乌克兰问题上的合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/biden-to-visit-france-for-meeting-with-macron-ahead-of-summits</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示，特朗普式的保守党对斯塔默年龄的攻击适得其反</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/trump-style-tory-attacks-on-starmer-s-age-backfired-poll-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项民意调查发现，首相里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 领导的保守党试图效仿唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的做法，攻击工党领袖基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 的年龄，但这一努力没有成功，资深保守党人批评了英国竞选活动中使用的美式言论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/trump-style-tory-attacks-on-starmer-s-age-backfired-poll-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 11:48:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国富人受通胀和高利率打击最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/britain-s-richest-hit-most-by-inflation-and-high-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于抵押贷款成本高昂以及餐馆和酒店价格快速上涨，英国最富裕家庭经历的通货膨胀率高于社会较贫困阶层。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/britain-s-richest-hit-most-by-inflation-and-high-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 10:54:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者对南非联合政府组合感到担忧，兰特下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/south-african-rand-drops-as-election-forecast-shows-anc-decline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非投资者原本预计选举结果将是执政的非洲人国民大会 (ANC) 能与一个较小党派联合执政。但有预测暗示 ANC 支持率将大幅下降，这打乱了投资者的预期，并引发了一系列不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/south-african-rand-drops-as-election-forecast-shows-anc-decline</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 06:59:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非进入未知领域，非洲人国民大会将分享权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/south-africa-s-anc-projected-to-lose-its-majority-model-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非执政党似乎将首次未能获得议会多数席位，这为该国下一届政府的组成带来了不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/south-africa-s-anc-projected-to-lose-its-majority-model-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 06:49:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
